License Overview:

There are 4 separate parts to the licensing of Absurd Saga.
1. All code and text are under the MIT license.
2. All images and graphics are under the CC0 Public Domain Dedication.
3. All music is under the Pixabay Content License.
4. The underlying Ren'Py game engine has its own licensing status.

